<recommendation type="For Fans" uid="296685">The presentation in every aspect is fantastic and some of the best I`ve seen. Sadly everything related to the story, plot and characters misses the mark completely and makes it hard to recommend that you actually sit down and watch the whole thing, maybe just watch clips of it.</recommendation>
<recommendation type="Recommended" uid="554857">Absolutely mesmerizing piece of art. The story does not give clear answers and is more about the sense of wonder and esoterical concepts beyond human grasp, but the audiovisual presentation was beyond stunning. Very recommended!</recommendation>
